---
title: Salisbury Steak Double Beef Meatballs with Mushroom Gravy, Peas and Smashed Potatoes
description: Hearty mushroom gravy smothers tender beef meatballs and comforting chive smashed potatoes in this modern take on Salisbury steak. In a word...YUM!
